数据的容器

----------------------------------------------


vector:

a = c(4,5,6)

a


常用的函数  in Base-R:
    vector(mode = 'logical',  length = 0)
    as.vector(x, mode = 'any')
    is.vector(x, mode = 'any')
-------------------------------------------------


matrix

m[row, col]: select an element

b = matrix(1:12 , 
            nrow = 3,
            byrow = F,    #默认为按列进行排列，故此应为默认值。
            dimnames = list(c('row1', 'row2', 'row3'), c('col1', 'col2', 'col3', ''))
)

